        "created_at": "2021-07-16T09:31:04.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>This has to be a negociant kind of wine produced by Raj Parr from grapes in Vosne Romanee.  You are required to be registered in France as a negociant and have a license etc.  Not sure about this one.   I would be interested.  Raj is into all kinds of projects.  Evening Land in the US is one of his projects.</p>",
